snippet.title: Come a little closer..
snippet.description:
We're here!
Download: https://discord.gg/6xeDBQSsjM

Forsaken AR is a modded APK/IPA for FNaF AR!
Forsaken AR allows you to unlock and trade modded characters, alongside other bug fixes and balances not present in the main game!

FNaF AR is the property of Illumix
FNaF is the property of Scott Cawthon

#fnafar #forsakenar #darkestdelivery
